---
title: Classic Chicken Schnitzel & Wedges with Creamy Slaw
description: Boost the flavour of a classic chicken schnitzel by adding our Aussie spice blend to the golden crumb coating. Served with garlic
aioli, potato fries and a creamy slaw for a meal nobody can refuse!
